title: Umno Youth to submit protest note to N Korean embassy
text:
More 
The murder of King Jong-nam has created diplomatic friction between Malaysia and North Korea, with both sides trading accusations. Tomorrow, Umno Youth would lead a delegation to submit a memorandum of protest to the North Korean embassy in Kuala Lumpur. In a text message to Malaysiakini , Umno Youth vice-chief Khairul Azwan Harun confirmed that he would be spearheading the group, which would also see the participation of BN Youth and other youth organisations. The gathering is slated for 4pm.
